@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_legyqw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs((0.41 - (v1 + 0.31 + tmp + 0.09)))
    tmp = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.52 / v1 + 0.72)) + (tmp / wp.abs(v1 + 0.65)))
    tmp = 0.81
    v1 = v0
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp + 0.80)) * 0.36)
    tmp = (wp.abs(v2) / (wp.cos(v0 + 0.32) * (tmp + 0.95 + tmp + 0.87)))
    tmp = v2
    data[tid] = v0
